author: SciShow
description:
In the 1920s, archaeologists discovered that the young pharaoh Tutankhamun was buried with a fancy iron dagger. It wasn't just fancy because part of it came from outer space; it was also made by artisans in another kingdom and given as a gift. But maybe not to Tut himself.

Hosted by: Savannah Geary (they/them)
